encapsulates the idea

20:05.472 --> 20:07.907
that natural water
is dangerous.

20:07.940 --> 20:10.343
Oh, well, how about
just that?

20:10.377 --> 20:11.844
How about, um...

20:11.878 --> 20:15.248
you know,
"Natural Water Isn't."

20:15.282 --> 20:19.486
When it is,
you can drink it,
but it's not right now.

20:19.519 --> 20:21.020
Maya:
I like that.

20:21.053 --> 20:22.755
You could just have,
"Because Natural Water Isn't,"

20:22.789 --> 20:23.923
