That's a good one, Thom.

20:27.627 --> 20:29.929
- You almost here?
- Um...

20:31.298 --> 20:33.500
no.

20:33.533 --> 20:35.768
We're still on the train.

20:35.802 --> 20:38.338
Just sitting here.

20:38.371 --> 20:40.640
We hit something
on the track.

20:40.673 --> 20:43.543
Gottfrid:
I hope they at least
killed it, yes, Thom?

20:43.576 --> 20:47.514
Jonathan:
Okay, uh, let's talk about
the presentation...

20:47.547 --> 20:50.550
Man on PA:
This is the last call
for 156,

20:50.583 --> 20:53.453
Southeast Scarborough
through South Fordham.

21:17.610 --> 21:20.380
