Here's what else happens
when you hit your 40s.

21:20.413 --> 21:23.383
You start thinking about
"The Outlaw Josey Wales."

21:23.416 --> 21:24.551
At least I did.

21:26.686 --> 21:28.888
Clint Eastwood, 1976.

