"Are you a bounty hunter?"

21:46.773 --> 21:48.841
The guy turns to him
and says,

21:48.875 --> 21:52.011
"A man's gotta do something
for a living these days."

21:52.044 --> 21:54.747
Josey sneers,
looks at him, and says,

21:54.781 --> 21:57.350
"Dyin' ain't
much of a living, boy."

21:57.384 --> 22:00.086
"Dying ain't much
of a living, boy."

22:00.119 --> 22:02.755
